{"id": 2566, "genre": 1001, "title": "从小到大你都有过哪些“懂规矩”的困扰？", "description": "有些规矩，也许只是那些墨守成规的家伙们自己跳不出，也不允许别人跳出的窠臼。（题图来自：iStock ©️CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 3072, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181019185400iUNzVlvRyp4ouLBI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-23T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 307968, "content": "上学要听老师的话，在家听老人的话，工作听领导的话……到了必须一个人决定的时候，又该听谁的话╯□╰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763503}, {"id": 306960, "content": "无时无刻要说对不起和谢谢\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145975}, {"id": 307734, "content": "一想到过年亲戚一起吃饭，又要挨个敬酒，就不想回家...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455584}, {"id": 307740, "content": "为什么一定要结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297840}, {"id": 306718, "content": "从小教育要听大人的话，要这样那样的，熟不知为什么不问问孩子的意见和建议呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482105}, {"id": 309033, "content": "学校领导要求的“表面”工程", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1494577}, {"id": 305967, "content": "什么规律？跪就对了", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875173}, {"id": 305968, "content": "陪客户吃饭的一切....简直就是折磨。", "image": null, "praise_count": 120, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177090}, {"id": 305969, "content": "交谈必须看着人\n吃饭不能吧唧嘴\n必须要用不好意思和谢谢（哪怕情况相反）", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1229774}, {"id": 306225, "content": "不能出去玩过了，什么是过了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904410}, {"id": 305972, "content": "上课要听老师话，即使是屁话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 188, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404922}, {"id": 305973, "content": "该不该叫姐？她究竟比我大几岁？叫姐会不会不合适？", "image": "img/option/option/20181023112657Dg7OJCBxRwKQF8pc", "praise_count": 140, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026252}, {"id": 305975, "content": "称呼你和“您”", "image": null, "praise_count": 260, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 305976, "content": "餐桌上长辈不动筷，孩子不能先吃；长辈不落座，孩子不能先坐", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1478223}, {"id": 305977, "content": "公共场合不能吃东西，然后买的饼，因为太忙赶路，公交车，地铁，教室。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288677}, {"id": 307257, "content": "女人的衣服不能晾外边显眼的位置", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147099}, {"id": 305978, "content": "双重标准", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668570}, {"id": 305979, "content": "社团聚餐，学弟要给学长敬酒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218456}, {"id": 306747, "content": "讨厌聚餐喝酒 各种餐桌礼节，油腻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462597}, {"id": 305980, "content": "吃饭要最后入座 “抢着”为饭桌上的人盛饭 最后动筷 圆桌也讲究座位 吃饱了也要坐着等所有人吃完才能离开 就算是简单的家庭聚餐（微笑脸）", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1463390}, {"id": 305982, "content": "吃饭不吧唧嘴不是算是繁文缛节吧，我觉得这是要遵守的基本礼仪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 220, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 412717}, {"id": 305983, "content": "吃饭吧唧嘴真的很没有礼貌 我觉得。这真是没规矩的表现", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755738}, {"id": 305984, "content": "和在追我的男孩子吃饭 即使真的不情愿 也不好意思提出我买单或者AA的请求 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755738}, {"id": 306240, "content": "叫姐姐还是叫阿姨😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1480023}, {"id": 305985, "content": "和领导长辈碰杯，杯子要比他们的低，我枯了", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162821}, {"id": 305986, "content": "你都这么大了，要懂规矩了", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1388915}, {"id": 305987, "content": "晦气话一个词都不能提，恨不得见谁都说您要活一百岁", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894776}, {"id": 305989, "content": "长辈说话，小辈的可不能有意见哟！", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334651}, {"id": 305990, "content": "给大人盛饭一定要双手递过去", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696088}, {"id": 305991, "content": "上班先帮领导洗茶杯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479768}, {"id": 305992, "content": "大部分规矩用于划分阶层，满足虚荣心，权利感，掌握感。用于满足自我的被需求被尊重感和归属感。它源于历史和社会发展，就像脊梁上的肿瘤。", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479765}, {"id": 305994, "content": "走亲戚时父母老是在亲戚面前问我有没有叫谁谁谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475848}, {"id": 305995, "content": "我真的不喜欢喝酒  别劝了靴靴", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956551}, {"id": 305997, "content": "与品牌方对接，该叫XX哥/姐还是直呼其名", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393055}, {"id": 305998, "content": "对面的到底是我的哪家亲戚，我该叫她七大姑还是八大姨？", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1430197}, {"id": 306510, "content": "毕业论文毫无意义，还是要写", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1426326}, {"id": 306000, "content": "别人打你是别人的错，你要是反手就是你的错", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1416398}, {"id": 306513, "content": "所谓的酒桌文化，真的让人很尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1426326}, {"id": 306002, "content": "见到不熟不亲甚至不认识的亲戚都被迫让喊人……不论多大，只要晚一秒叫人，就会被说你是哑巴", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454682}, {"id": 306003, "content": "能自己解决的尽量别麻烦别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479822}, {"id": 306004, "content": "下楼梯，领导先下，还是走的快的先下~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1370491}, {"id": 306005, "content": "用筷子和汤勺要用右手？逼死左撇子？左右通用也不对？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429934}, {"id": 306006, "content": "据理力争还是默不出声", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475652}, {"id": 306007, "content": "该不该反驳领导？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982279}, {"id": 306009, "content": "食不言，寝不语", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377387}, {"id": 306010, "content": "吃饭什么该吃什么不该吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469720}, {"id": 306011, "content": "要听上层的修改意见。  上层：你是设计 你的想法呢 。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972975}, {"id": 306012, "content": "一定要恭维领导？（IT从业人员）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479446}, {"id": 306013, "content": "过年拿到红包不能马上拆Ծ‸ Ծ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479512}, {"id": 306014, "content": "关于我自己吃饭，用筷子的方式跟主流的用法不一样，难道我这么用，会把饭塞进鼻孔里吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479898}]}